{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li0 \fi0 _x000D__x000D_ _x000D__x000D_ Catherine Hays Zabriskie is the Associate Director of Academic Technology for the College of Arts and Humanities. She supports ARHU faculty in their use of technology in teaching and research. Catherine coordinates the College's {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "www.arhu.umd.edu/technology/workshops/index.html"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Digital Technology in the Arts and Humanities
}}}
 learning opportunities for faculty. In addition, Catherine is available to meet with faculty for individual project consulting and software tutoring. She coordinates the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "www.arhu.umd.edu/utap/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Undergraduate Technology Apprenticeship
}}}
 program for the College as well as other projects such as the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "www.arhu.umd.edu/vislit/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Visual Literacy Toolbox
}}}
._x000D__x000D_ _x000D__x000D_\par}
